<HEAD>Sudden Change In Youth Arrested in Quadruple Ax Murder Puzzles
Police</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: LEADS with two grafs to add missing `a' in 2nd graf; PICKS UP
3rd graf pvs, `There's a ...' INSERTS one graf after 4th graf pvs,
`Brom appeared ...' to ADD psychiatric exam ordered; SUBS grafs 7,
